    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Indeed every data we pass to user functions should be cloned. An easy and performant cloning mechanism is JSON.parse(JSON.stringify()).\n\nOther cloning method are really big with a lot of cases. Since we know it's pure parsed JSON then we should be safe with JSON.parse(JSON.stringify()).\n\nSpots:\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/6ce160b7505a21fd16b3207b8f37b658c2e120b5/src/components/Template.js#L100\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/6ce160b7505a21fd16b3207b8f37b658c2e120b5/src/components/Template.js#L71\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/6ce160b7505a21fd16b3207b8f37b658c2e120b5/src/components/Template.js#L75\n",
