    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Even if we should clone data, I wonder how this can happen\n\nReally simplified:\n\n```\nfunction clearRefinement(helper, refinement) {\n  helper.clearRefinement(refinement.attributeName, refinement.name);\n}\nlet refinement = { name: 'val' };\nlet handleClick = clearRefinement.bind(helper, refinement);\n<Template onClick={handleClick} templateData={refinement} transformData={(data) => { data.name = 'notval'; return data; }} />\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2015-11-24T15:31:01Z",
